snippet.title: World's very funniest and cutest babies & kids - Compilation of the best moments
snippet.description:
Super funny, hilarious and cute compilation about babies, toddlers and kids! I'm sure this compilation will make you laugh and smile! Here are the funniest sleepy kids, toddlers making funny faces, laughing babies, funny fails, pranks,... . How do you like it? Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
